null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Allah will say: ‘O Fatima! I swear by My honor and My glory! I have sworn to Myself two thousand years before the creation of the Heavens and the Earth, that I shall not punish your Shia and Shia of your progeny in the hell-fire.’", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Us waqt Allah-taala ki jaanib se wahee aayegi, ay Fatema Mujhe apni izzat o jalaal aur buland maqaam ki qasam, zameen o aasmaan ki khilqat mein do hazaar (2000) saal qabl apne zaat ki qasam khaai hai. Mai tere aur tere khaandaan ke dosto’n ko Jahannam ka azaab nahi dunga.", "UrduDescription": "اس وقت اللہ تعالیٰ کی جانب سے وحی آئے گی۔ اے فاطمہ مجھے اپنی عزّت و جلال اور بلند مقام کی قسم زمین و آسمان کی خلقت میں دو ہزار سال قبل اپنی ذات کی قسم کھائی ہے۔ میں تیرے اور تیرے خاندان کے دوستوں کو جہنم کا عذاب نہیں دوں گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlu